Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了这可能是真家伙吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为脑中的景象很鲜明嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  你实在是太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么像这样的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本先生马上打开客厅的门进入这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也搞不清楚  说是预定变更了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  一脸像看到幽灵的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么愿望都能实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法笔记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给别人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大概是在一个月之前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  打扰您休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发现了您的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能将那罕见的能力借给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我打算送给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续十次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不会错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本笔记能够操控机率  改变未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是超能力的一种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够随心所欲地操控未来  那确实是最强了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是有人想对那些孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就说不通了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接在笔记上写不是更快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因为LV太低而起不了那么大的作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能期待太大的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须从小事一点一点地积累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小气的规则啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大小的标准是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我测试过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}贤木修二得到巨大的财富
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真这么写了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人都会写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么结果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在皆本的公寓捡到这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小气！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我掉的一千日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本先生也好小气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提  我们也试着写了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:09.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}常盘奈津子  和贝克汉姆约会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}野分萤  挖出石油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有发生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该把管理官叫来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的话  也没那么紧急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我再调查看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了  皆本君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  Children呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在待机室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是有功课要做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近都很忙  没怎么睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那么有什么新发现就通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}规则4
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}从笔记上撕下的页面也是能够使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些从笔记上偷偷地撕下来的页面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管写什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能一个人独占皆本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为皆本先生只有一个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果我们都这么写的话  会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:06.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}规则5
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果写下了无法同时成立的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么新写的内容优先实现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人中有一个人写的会实现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们已经约好了  都不会写的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会写的  这两个家伙肯定会写的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都来劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是真刀真枪的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我都要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你们不写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们在找机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了  这两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须想点办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用念力打倒她们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  这样马上就会穿帮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后写的内容优先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能让她们知道我什么时候写
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是智力战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一算  必须严加警戒的是——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样的进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.75,0:10:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们犯了致命的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  我真不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太笨了  所以想不出什么特别的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先写增加零用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:58.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}零用钱增加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:58.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}希望葵和紫穗永远幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真为自己感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就写这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}让胸部变大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}希望薰和紫穗能遇到很多好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要写
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}愿自己的心灵更加纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}希望小薰和小葵永远是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是挚友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始写作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  待会借我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先吃点零食
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都小看我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才写的不过是普通的纸片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把笔记上的纸片发给三人的时候确实都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只把自己的偷换成假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧妙的作战方案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵和紫穗突然睡意袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来的时候忘记了笔记的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:11:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大端先生您有这份心意  我就很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我要去准备晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这个世上还有一本  「如愿以偿笔记」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}チルチルは僕も好きだよ{\r}\N我也喜欢ChiRuChiRu哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}如愿以偿记事本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}How to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}<规则1>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}这本笔记上所述之事\N有高几率成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}但只限可能发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}<规则2>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}写入时脑中浮现的\N景象越鲜明\N  实现的几率就越高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}<规则3>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}不要太过期待\N实现大的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}从小事开始累积
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}<规则4>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}笔记中取下的碎片\N也能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}<规则5>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs28}所述愿望产生矛盾\N之时 以后载者为准
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}読めるけど書けない{\r}\N会念不会写
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还有一本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋在那棵树下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析已经结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去了下厕所而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着笔记去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本是不会做这样的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把笔记放下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能没发现笔记被撕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你却不在意Children的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你不是皆本  那么就是有能力冒充他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这种超能力者是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然笔记的影响力并不大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡意突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  至少能够帮助我进入B.A.B.E.L
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这本笔记没有把皆本那么快叫回来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}贤木修二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}因为疲劳而昏倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止都在我的计划之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又热又潮湿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我忍受不了老年人的体臭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭的是笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枉我还当你们是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话原封不动还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们全都睡了快一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过笔记似乎没有消除记忆的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不准偷跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去房里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  只有医生在？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本先生去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法读取这一两小时内的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笔记也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么应该是在局长或者婆婆那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们俩还没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在用瞬移…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的约定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  睡相真难看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太粗俗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人都活了几十年了还跟小孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有资格说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就把B.A.B.E.L.的所有系统都改写了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的资料也换成假的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们再也无法侦测到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是这次的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便还发现了限制器解除用手机的备用品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再神通广大  也无法阻止我入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我做好随时被袭击的觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在把B.A.B.E.L.灭掉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  我现在想好好玩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始裁决了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本先生强烈爱上The Children的其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管谁被选上  其他人都不准怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢我们中的谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在说什么傻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂姆和巴雷特失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是黑色幽灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是洗脑没有完全解除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么必须要快点去救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  Children出动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Children解禁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚心许愿的话就一定会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃你的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的心意能改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对可怜Children
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个混蛋  藏哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还和黑色幽灵有牵连吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大端先生说的能够实现愿望改变未来的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老爷爷可能是信口开河吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是信口开河
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有愿望的话  就写在这上面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:25.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}取回记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}恢复失去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想取回记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己的名字都不知道   实在无法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是失去的记忆恢复了的话  肯定会更加痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和他一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚出去  怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐隐约约地知道过去的回忆都是些痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了一切的我没有想要实现的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说没有任何愿望这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  那么这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}希望两人能够交到好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  不坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你好久了  这个是蒂姆你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是虎Mate的限定ChiRuChiRu挂链手办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不瞒你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝对ChiRuChiRu的公认网站的管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你是「ChiRuChiRu是我的老婆」先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是昨天一起做实况的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你是…「ChiRuChiRu好可爱啊ChiRuChiRu」君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心之友人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:19:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们半夜不睡原来是因为这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉异常地兴奋起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴致好高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看上去非常意气相投啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟笔记上写的一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是笔记的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此许愿的人不是你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让超能力者…\N让他人获得幸福可能就是你们的超能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  皆本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没回答要选择我们中的谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆点回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说什么傻话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你们三人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准用这招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时认真回答是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会寂寞地跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点长大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候我会给出答案的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的在等待那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为此才活到现在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉和平时不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个皆本先生好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是萌？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在萌吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它什么公平竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我写
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰  我愿意为此去死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在骗我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在玩些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情处理完了就早点回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老头居然写了这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:57.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}拿走笔记的人在有效期限内尽情玩乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:21:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效日期是到今天吧  一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心了  那两个人能变得有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有些担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然先把大端先生埋的笔记挖出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我本来就打算给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你已经写好愿望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  已经写了三个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是  希望明天也是个好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.91,0:21:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  希望洗掉的衣物能快点干
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后是  能做出好吃的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太贪心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的愿望确实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.40,0:21:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,细微地实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微早点回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:22:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然搞错了去参加了精锐部队的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.50,0:22:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副模样回来也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起看啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的绝对可怜Children是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  三位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.35,0:23:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜升级
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.32,0:23:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又长大一点了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵部少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.34,0:23:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有地方和平时不同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有地方是什么地方啊  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都想和你们一起庆祝你们的成长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.69,0:23:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会陪我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对可怜Children
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.62,0:24:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第47话  「一场春梦！明日的回忆」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆本…那家伙来了之后一切都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.36,0:24:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.16,0:24:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰  这样下去你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对可怜  所以不会输！
